definition: name/noun (part of speech)/place (e.g. among winners)/famous/classifier for people
exterior surface/family relationship via females/to show (one's opinion)/a model/a table (listing information)/a form/a meter (measuring sth)

sentences.english: Entry form will be destroyed before the commencement of next Music Festival.
sentences.chinese: 报名表将于来届音乐节开始前销毁。

sentences.english: Please complete registration form below and turn into your teacher or PTA .
sentences.chinese: 请详细填写报名表后交给班级老师或家长会。

sentences.english: Entry form is invalid if not properly completed or with insufficient supporting materials.
sentences.chinese: 报名表填写不清或资料不齐者，一概视为无效。

sentences.english: Please read the Notes before Application before filling out this application form.
sentences.chinese: 填写报名表前，请先详读招生简章上的报名注意事项。

sentences.english: Hm, thank you. Now, please fill in this form.
sentences.chinese: 完成交费的考生，请填写好报名表，填好后提交。

sentences.english: I filled in the form and wrote down typing as my training course.
sentences.chinese: 我填写了报名表，并写下了打字作为我的培训科目。

sentences.english: Add or revise the content in the On-line Application Form.
sentences.chinese: 可以添加或者修改您的网上报名表的内容。

sentences.english: The reprography of this form can be used.
Upon completion of your payment, please proceed to fill out the GRE online registration form and submit it.
sentences.chinese: 完成交费的考生，请填写好报名表，填好后提交。

sentences.english: I declare that all information provided in this Enrollment form is, to the best of my knowledge, accurate and complete.
sentences.chinese: 本人声明于本报名表所提供资料均属真确，并无遗漏。

sentences.english: I affirm that the facts set forth in it are true and complete.
sentences.chinese: 本人谨此声明在本报名表填报的资料均属正确。

sentences.english: Comes from power department's games application form.
sentences.chinese: 来自动力部门的运动会报名表。

sentences.english: Please mail back this form together with all personal application forms.
sentences.chinese: 请連同各赛员个人报名表一并寄回。

sentences.english: There is no charge to download and complete the Electronic Diversity Visa Entry Form.
sentences.chinese: 有免费下载并填写报名表电子多样性签证。

sentences.english: I confirm that all the information I write above is true.
sentences.chinese: 我确认我在本报名表中所提供的信息均属真实有效。

sentences.english: Your Registration will be regarded as your promise to be present at the workshop.
sentences.chinese: 一旦发来报名表，则视为对参加工作坊全程的承诺。

definition: to sign up/to enter one's name/to apply/to register/to enroll/to enlist
to fill in a form/to write data in a box (on a questionnaire or web form)
receipt (written acknowledgement of receipt of an item)
